org.vertx.java.core.http

Class CaseInsensitiveMultiMap

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.vertx.java.core.http.CaseInsensitiveMultiMap
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<java.util.Map.Entry<java.lang.String,java.lang.String>>, MultiMap

    public final class CaseInsensitiveMultiMap
extends java.lang.Object
implements MultiMap
    This multi-map implementation has case insensitive keys, and can be used to hold some HTTP headers prior to making an HTTP request.
